  "description": "全球天气MCP服务器，支持中国城市和全球天气查询 - Global Weather MCP Server with support for Chinese cities",
  "main": "./build/index.js",
  "type": "module",
  "bin": {
    "mcp-weather": "./build/index.js"
  },
  "scripts": {
